These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: cola, lemonade, almond-milk, iced-tea, hot-chocolate, milk, mirinda
There are 7 different nationalities: spanish, brazilian, canadian, japanese, malaysian, colombian, turkish
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: badminton, rowing, rugby, biathlon, weightlifting, climbing, ice-hockey
The people use 7 different means of transport: bus, airplane, roller, snowmobile, car, trike, motorbike
 1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the japanese##1
 3. the person driving the car is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 4. the brazilian is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 5. the spanish is on the right of the turkish##1
 6. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 7. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the malaysian##1
 8. the person driving the snowmobile is between the person driving the motorbike and the colombian##2
 9. the malaysian is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
10. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle##1
11. the person who's sport is badminton is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
12. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person driving the bus##1
13. the person drinking cola is on the left of the canadian##1
14. the colombian is the person driving the roller##1
15. the person driving the trike is on the left of the turkish##1
16. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
17. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the canadian##1
18. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the malaysian##1
19. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Beverage      | lemonade  | milk        | hot-chocolate | almond-milk      | iced-tea     | cola      | mirinda     |
